Most people probably don't know what I'm saying.

107
00:12:04,095 --> 00:12:05,395
え、どういうことだ？
Eh, what does it mean?

108
00:12:05,595 --> 00:12:08,295
3からの4、からの...
From 3 to 4, from...

109
00:12:08,595 --> 00:12:09,395
え？
Eh?

110
00:12:11,495 --> 00:12:13,495
なんだろう、なんで1じゃないんだろう。
I wonder... why isn't it 1?

111
